  "body" : "<p>I am interating through classes in a Jar file and wish to find those which are not abstract. I can solve this by instantiating the classes and trapping InstantiationException but that has a performance hit as some classes have heavy startup. I can't find anything obviously like isAbstract() in the Class.java docs.</p>\n"
